&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;The Senior Data Management Developer will play a key role within the data management team. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;They will be involved in gathering user requirements, data extraction, report building, data warehouse management and also help manage, train and mentor more junior team members within the data management team. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;We are looking for an enthusiastic individual with drive and commitment, who is motivated by achieving, empowering and informing. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;Applicants must have experience in handling clinical/sensitive information and manipulating large datasets within complex computer software; good communication, interpersonal, organisational skills and good SQL, Reporting Services, MS Excel skills.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
